<h3>Learning Outcomes</h3>

A <i>learning outcome</i> is a goal whose achievement is expected. Because
achievement depends fundamentally on desire and work ethic, it follows
that learning outcomes vary among individuals. Learning outcomes for
this course constitute a full range, from low to high degree, of
progress toward course goals.
